Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "#   â€¢ TachyonFX animations"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "#   â€¢ Screen streaming support"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "#   â€¢ Vim-like navigation"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "#   â€¢ Beautiful Android green theme"
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "# Install: cargo install droidtui"
Sleep 2s
